Package: rayvista
Type: Package
Title: A {rayshader} plugin to simplify plotting 3d elevation with map overlays.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Hugh",
           family = "Graham",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "hugh.a.graham@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9451-5010"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: This package provides a simple function to plot the elvation around
  a given lat lon location with a specified sarch radius with a map overlay draped
  over the terrain. terrain data is aquired via {elevatr} and map data is from 
  {maptiles}.
